request.description:
Custom route. Upload a CSV file (max 5 MB) with product data. Required columns:
title, handle, description, variant_sku, price_inr, price_usd, stock, material, size, finish, wood_type, dimensions, warranty

Returns: { summary: { total_rows, created, updated, skipped, failed }, details }

